        "description": {
            "value": "<p>This wooden staff is remarkably sturdy and unyielding. While wielding the staff, you gain a +1 circumstance bonus to your DC to avoid being shoved or tripped.</p>\n<p><strong>Activate</strong> Cast a Spell</p>\n<hr />\n<p><strong>Effect</strong> You expend a number of charges from the staff to cast a spell from its list.</p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Cantrip</strong> <em>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.Shield]</em></li>\n<li><strong>1st</strong> <em>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.Alarm], @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.Mystic Armor]</em></li>\n<li><strong>2nd</strong> <em>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.Dispel Magic], @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.Environmental Endurance], @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.Resist Energy]</em></li>\n<li><strong>3rd</strong> <em>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.Alarm], @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.Safe Passage]</em></li>\n<li><strong>4th</strong> <em>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.Dispel Magic], @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.Mystic Armor], @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.Resist Energy]</em></li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Craft Requirements</strong> Supply one casting of all listed ranks of all listed spells.</p>"
